Package org.logevents.optional.jakarta

Class HttpServletResponseMDC

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.logevents.optional.jakarta.HttpServletResponseMDC
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DynamicMDC
    public class HttpServletResponseMDC
extends Object
implements DynamicMDC
    Populates MDC or JSON format according to Elastic Common Schema guidelines:
    • http.response.status_code: HttpServletResponse.getStatus()
    • http.response.mime_type: ServletResponse.getContentType()
    • http.response.redirect: "Location" response header
